      "content": "Wait, 15 minutes by train between Marunouchi and Shibuya seems a bit low. Is that correct? Also, could you expand on the Shibuya part? I need a more detailed breakdown of the travel times/routes and maybe a few more cafe options where it's actually quiet? Shibuya can get pretty intense.",
